b'{"data_headers":{"result_code":1},"data":{"information":{"article_id":890,"category_name":"News","pr_category_id":"1","title_name":"Regarding Balance Adjustments for Certain Quests[Update]","message":"<div><span style=\\"color: rgb(44, 130, 201);\\"><strong>[Update <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1574927700\\"><\/span>]<br><\/strong><\/span>After the data update is applied around <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1575005400\\"><\/span>, you will be able to use auto-play when playing solo for each difficulty of High Zodiark&#39;s Trial and co-op for Prelude difficulty.<br><br>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.<br><br><\/div><hr><div>We will be making balance adjustments to certain quests in a data update to be applied around <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1574920800\\"><\/span>.<\/div><div>The details are as follows.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div><strong>\\u25a0Quests<\/strong><\/div><div>\\u30fbAvenue to Fortune<\/div><div>\\u30fbDragon Trials<\/div><div>\\u30fbThe Imperial Onslaught<\/div><div>\\u30fbAdvanced Dragon Trials<\/div><div>\\u30fbVoid Battles<\/div><div>\\u30fbAstral Raids<\/div><div><br><\/div><div><strong>\\u25a0Adjustments<\/strong><\/div><div>1. Avenue to Fortune<\/div><div>\\u30fbWe will increase the number of rupies that can be obtained as drop rewards for each difficulty.<\/div><div>\\u30fbWe will increase the number of rupies that can be obtained as a daily bonus for each difficulty.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>2. Dragon Trials<\/div><div>\\u30fbIt will be possible to use skip tickets on Master difficulty for each quest.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>3. The Imperial Onslaught<\/div><div>\\u30fbIt will be possible to use skip tickets on Master difficulty for each quest.<\/div><div>\\u30fbWe will adjust the drop rates for rewards on all difficulties for each quest.<\/div><div>You will be able to get more material items, such as sword tablets, azure insignias, and Dyrenell Argenteus.<\/div><div>\\u30fbWe will increase the number of material items that can be obtained as a daily bonus for all difficulties on each quest.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>4. Advanced Dragon Trials<\/div><div>\\u30fbWe will reduce the amount of getherwings consumed when playing the Prelude and Standard difficulties for each quest.<\/div><div>The amount consumed for Prelude difficulty will change from three to two, and for Standard difficulty it will change from five to three.<\/div><div>\\u30fbWe will greatly increase the number of rupies that can be obtained as drop rewards for each quest on Standard, Expert, and Master difficulty.<\/div><div>\\u30fbWe will add the fortifying crystal, amplifying crystal, fortifying gemstone, and amplifying gemstone material items, which can confer augments, to the drop rewards for each quest on Standard, Expert, and Master difficulty.<\/div><div>Quests will always drop a total of three material items that can confer augments.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>5. Void Battles<\/div><div>\\u30fbWe will increase the number of rupies that can be obtained as drop rewards for certain quests.<\/div><div>\\u30fbWe will add the fortifying crystal, amplifying crystal, fortifying gemstone, and amplifying gemstone material items, which can confer augments, to the drop rewards for certain quests.<\/div><div>Quests will always drop one material item that can confer augments.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>The Void Battle quests that will receive these balance adjustments are as follows.<\/div><div>\\u30fbSmoldering Manticore Strike<\/div><div>\\u30fbGreedy Manticore Strike<\/div><div>\\u30fbRaging Manticore Strike<\/div><div>\\u30fbVoid Zephyr Strike<\/div><div>\\u30fbVoid Poseidon Strike<\/div><div>\\u30fbVoid Jeanne d&#39;Arc Strike<\/div><div>\\u30fbVoid Nidhogg Strike<\/div><div>\\u30fbVoid Agni Strike<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>6. Astral Raids<\/div><div>The following two adjustments will be applied starting with the Astral Raids beginning <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1575093600\\"><\/span>.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u30fbIn future Astral Raids, we will increase the drop rates in Expert and Master difficulty for the fortifying crystal, amplifying crystal, fortifying gemstone, and amplifying gemstone material items, which can confer augments.<\/div><div>The material items you can obtain will vary each time Astral Raids are live.<\/div><div>\\u30fbIn future Astral Raids, we will increase the number of astral shards that drop in Master difficulty.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>7. Other<\/div><div>\\u30fbWhile Astral Raids are active, a 60 Astral Piece Set will be added to the shop.<\/div><div>\\u30fbWhile Astral Raids are active, a 30 Astral Piece Set will be added to the shop.<\/div><div>\\u30fbThe 60 Astral Piece Set that was previously available while Astral Raids were active will no longer be available.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>The following three adjustments will be applied starting <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1575180000\\"><\/span>.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u30fbWe will increase the maximum amount of material items you can trade for using astral shards in the Treasure Trade for Astral Raids.<\/div><div>\\u30fbWe will add Rupies to the rewards you can trade for using astral shards in the Treasure Trade for Astral Raids.<\/div><div>\\u30fbWe will increase the number of rupies you can trade for using void leaves in the Treasure Trade for Void Battles.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.<\/div>","start_time":1574316000,"prev_article_id":"872","next_article_id":"894","image_path":"","update_time":1574927604}}}'